WEBVTT

00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:55.740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

00:00:56.820 --> 00:00:59.780
=Episode 15=
=Don't Touch My Woman!=

00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:08.800
Miaomiao!

00:01:10.720 --> 00:01:11.560
Don't come over.

00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:13.720
Why are you here?

00:01:14.240 --> 00:01:15.360
To watch me fall apart?

00:01:15.360 --> 00:01:16.200
Miaomiao.

00:01:16.210 --> 00:01:17.060
Calm down, please.

00:01:17.070 --> 00:01:17.910
Come over here first.

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:18.790
Shut up.

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:20.240
It was you.

00:01:20.840 --> 00:01:21.960
You took Hu Yitong away.

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:23.760
And now my brother too?

00:01:23.760 --> 00:01:24.630
Miaomiao.

00:01:24.680 --> 00:01:25.520
Please, calm down.

00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:28.480
Miaomiao!

00:01:28.680 --> 00:01:30.240
- Miaomiao!
- Miaomiao!

00:01:30.240 --> 00:01:31.200
Stay back.

00:01:31.440 --> 00:01:32.280
Miaomiao.

00:01:32.280 --> 00:01:33.840
I'm not a thief.

00:01:33.840 --> 00:01:35.960
Why won't they believe me?

00:01:35.960 --> 00:01:37.400
I know you're not the thief.

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:38.240
Miaomiao.

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:40.240
Come over first, please. Okay?

00:01:40.240 --> 00:01:41.320
Miaomiao, come over.

00:01:41.320 --> 00:01:42.920
I'll explain everything to them.

00:01:43.240 --> 00:01:44.760
I don't want to see her.

00:01:45.840 --> 00:01:47.400
Tell her to leave.

00:01:47.400 --> 00:01:48.960
- Okay.
- Now!

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:51.320
I'll ask her to go.

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:58.040
Miaomiao.

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:04.440
It's alright now.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:06.840
It's all fine now.

00:02:16.760 --> 00:02:17.600
Xibei.

00:02:18.600 --> 00:02:19.760
Say what's on your mind.

00:02:20.320 --> 00:02:21.280
Um…

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:22.840
Boss, he…

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:28.400
Boss's matters aren't ours to handle.

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:29.640
Weren't those your exact words?

00:02:32.080 --> 00:02:33.760
Anyway, we see this kind of drama happening

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:34.520
every single day.

00:02:35.240 --> 00:02:36.080
Look.

00:02:37.260 --> 00:02:40.500
(Warning: Detected
abnormal emotional fluctuation.)

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:41.720
But Boss is still the boss.

00:02:41.720 --> 00:02:43.440
Why did you lock
Maimai's and my data?

00:02:43.680 --> 00:02:44.520
If

00:02:44.520 --> 00:02:46.440
you're helping Boss,

00:02:46.440 --> 00:02:47.760
then stay focused.

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:50.760
This feels like a personal vendetta.

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:51.840
I admit it.

00:02:52.160 --> 00:02:53.440
That day, I was emotional.

00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:54.960
Got a little carried away.

00:02:57.640 --> 00:02:59.200
Don't forget that agreement we singed

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:00.440
before joining Keep Love.

00:03:00.960 --> 00:03:02.320
No dating allowed.

00:03:02.760 --> 00:03:04.600
But Boss is dating more than any of us.

00:03:04.600 --> 00:03:05.440
What can I say?

00:03:06.240 --> 00:03:07.400
Hopeless.

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:13.640
Xibei.

00:03:14.480 --> 00:03:15.840
Xibei.

00:03:18.920 --> 00:03:19.760
Have some water.

00:03:33.800 --> 00:03:34.640
Brother.

00:03:36.760 --> 00:03:38.440
Did you really marry Ding Daang?

00:03:41.960 --> 00:03:42.800
So you don't have to

00:03:43.480 --> 00:03:45.360
worry about Hu Yitong
bothering her anymore.

00:03:46.200 --> 00:03:47.680
I want to know that you did this

00:03:48.520 --> 00:03:49.640
to help me

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:52.800
or to improve Keep Love's data.

00:03:53.560 --> 00:03:55.840
Hu Yitong is indeed
my most suitable match.

00:03:57.960 --> 00:03:59.560
But do you really like Ding Daang?

00:04:00.200 --> 00:04:01.160
Don't ask questions.

00:04:05.160 --> 00:04:06.160
I know you remember

00:04:07.200 --> 00:04:08.560
everything,

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:11.360
including the time, place, and items.

00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:13.640
You recall them perfectly.

00:04:14.440 --> 00:04:15.920
Like reciting from a textbook.

00:04:17.080 --> 00:04:19.480
But I can't feel any warmth
from you anymore.

00:04:21.200 --> 00:04:22.520
The way you look at me feels like

00:04:22.520 --> 00:04:24.000
you're staring at a test subject.

00:04:27.780 --> 00:04:30.700
(Advice: Your caress may appease her.)

00:04:43.520 --> 00:04:44.360
Miaomiao.

00:04:46.440 --> 00:04:47.880
I've just been so busy lately.

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:49.840
I've neglected you.

00:04:51.840 --> 00:04:52.800
Can you forgive me?

00:05:00.800 --> 00:05:01.840
I'll make sure

00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:06.520
Hu Yitong comes back to you.

00:05:08.360 --> 00:05:09.800
That's my promise to you.

00:05:13.480 --> 00:05:14.320
Trust me.

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:31.240
Ruomai.

00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:35.000
Do you think I'm being foolish?

00:05:37.040 --> 00:05:38.720
I was ready for all of this.

00:05:41.440 --> 00:05:44.000
But my heart still aches so much.

00:05:47.920 --> 00:05:50.280
He's like ice that never warms.

00:05:51.640 --> 00:05:52.840
Every time

00:05:52.840 --> 00:05:54.560
when things are about to get better,

00:05:57.080 --> 00:05:59.240
it all falls back to square one.

00:06:00.320 --> 00:06:02.320
But at least he has changed.

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:03.560
Right?

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:06.680
Changed?

00:06:08.360 --> 00:06:10.120
Those tiny little changes

00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:13.360
are like glitches popping up

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:15.400
by chance in a program.

00:06:17.480 --> 00:06:18.760
Stop drinking.

00:06:20.400 --> 00:06:22.320
He's not worth it.

00:06:22.920 --> 00:06:24.760
He's like a heartless AI.

00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:27.680
Men's passion never lasts.

00:06:28.440 --> 00:06:29.800
Don't let yourself get stuck again.

00:06:29.800 --> 00:06:30.760
Pull yourself together.

00:06:33.440 --> 00:06:35.080
He's not some AI.

00:06:35.800 --> 00:06:36.920
He's no AI.

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:39.120
He's my Aming.

00:06:43.400 --> 00:06:44.640
Stop drinking!

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.080
I'll take you home.

00:06:47.080 --> 00:06:48.520
I'm not going home.

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:50.560
I have no home.

00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:52.280
I have no home.

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:54.280
I have no home.

00:06:55.200 --> 00:06:56.320
I have no home!

00:06:58.240 --> 00:06:59.240
I have no home.

00:07:04.920 --> 00:07:07.720
Go and bring my Aming back right now.

00:07:08.080 --> 00:07:09.000
Bring Aming back to me.

00:07:09.000 --> 00:07:10.000
Did you hear that?

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:10.880
Hurry up!

00:07:11.060 --> 00:07:12.160
Find him and bring him here.

00:07:12.760 --> 00:07:13.600
I'm on it.

00:07:14.160 --> 00:07:15.880
My passion can last forever.

00:07:16.280 --> 00:07:19.120
Even love gurus
lose their touch sometimes.

00:07:26.440 --> 00:07:28.480
Would you risk everything
to love someone?

00:07:32.200 --> 00:07:33.040
I would.

00:07:33.790 --> 00:07:34.680
Why?

00:07:34.800 --> 00:07:36.160
Because I met the right person.

00:07:36.880 --> 00:07:38.200
What makes someone the right one?

00:07:39.960 --> 00:07:41.440
Someone who can unlock my code.

00:07:43.280 --> 00:07:45.640
What if she's someone empty inside?

00:07:45.920 --> 00:07:46.860
I'll fill it with love.

00:07:48.600 --> 00:07:49.760
What if...

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:51.580
you can't fill that emptiness?

00:07:58.560 --> 00:07:59.480
I'll keep going.

00:08:07.800 --> 00:08:08.640
Ding Daang.

00:08:08.840 --> 00:08:10.000
