00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:22.840
Don't touch my woman.

00:08:32.760 --> 00:08:34.080
Aming.

00:08:38.920 --> 00:08:40.680
Aming.

00:08:41.640 --> 00:08:42.920
Aming.

00:08:43.360 --> 00:08:45.080
Please, don't leave me.

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:48.440
Aming.

00:08:49.400 --> 00:08:51.680
Please, don't leave me, okay?

00:08:55.320 --> 00:08:56.800
If you're going to leave,

00:08:57.880 --> 00:08:59.320
