00:09:00.760 --> 00:09:02.560
Let's leave together.

00:09:04.640 --> 00:09:05.640
Chen Aming!

00:09:06.440 --> 00:09:08.120
In the future you've planned,

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:10.000
