00:09:15.760 --> 00:09:17.920
Why couldn't you come back
half a year earlier?

00:09:19.200 --> 00:09:20.440
Don't treat me like this.

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:24.640
If there's part of you that cares,

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:27.040
