00:12:31.000 --> 00:12:32.290
During the contract period,

00:12:33.040 --> 00:12:33.880
Party B

00:12:34.800 --> 00:12:35.640
must not

00:12:36.040 --> 00:12:38.440
have close contact with any man
other than Party A

00:12:38.440 --> 00:12:39.280
